  • Classes in Model used by Controller 
    Class and Description
    BookingHistory
    This class contains all information of the booking history - including its TID (Transaction ID), customer who made the booking and the seat booked.

    This class contains all information of a holiday - including its name, date and price rate.
    Movie
    This class contains all information of a movie - including its title, age restriction, director, synopsis, cast, status and ticket sales.
    Review
    This class contains all information of one piece of review - including the reviewing date, rating, reviewing content, reviewing Movie and reviewer's name.
    Showtime
    This class contains all information of a showtime - including its Movie, Cinema, Date and a 2D array of Seat.
